    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="IDcomponent" graphiccount="0">
        <title>TOWING</title>
        <para>Do not tow vehicles without first pulling the axles or disconnecting the driveshaft. Lubrication of the
            internal gear train is inadequate when the vehicle is towed.
        </para>
